Questions 36-37 refer to the following sort method.

```java
public static void sort(int arr[])
{
    int i;
    int num;
    int j;
    for (i = 1; i < arr.length; i++) /* outer loop */
    {
        num = arr[i];
        j = i - 1;
        while (j >= 0 && arr[j] > num) /* inner loop */
        {
            arr[j + 1] = arr[j];
            j = j - 1;
        }
        arr[j + 1] = num;
    }
}
```

